Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Beijing, March 7 (XINHUA) -- Chinese President Jiang 
joint communique concerning the basis of Sino-Azerbaijani 
friendly relations here this evening. 
  Six other documents between China and Azerbaijan were also 
signed on the occasion. They were the summary of agreements 
establishing air transportation, agreement on scientific and 
technological cooperation, agreement on cultural cooperation, 
agreement on sanitary and medical science cooperation, agreement 
on tourism exchange and agreement on broadcast, film and 
television cooperation. 

