<H3> <TI>   Vice Premier Li Lanqing Meets Indonesian Visitors </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  OW0803063694 Beijing XINHUA in English 0611 GMT 8 Mar 94 </F>
<F P=103> OW0803063694 </F>
<F P=104>  Beijing XINHUA </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Beijing, March 8 (XINHUA) -- Chinese Vice Premier Li 
Lanqing met with I.B. Sudjana, minister of mines and energy of 
Indonesia, and his party here this morning. 
  Chinese Minister of the Machine-Building Industry He 
Guangyuan took part in the meeting. 
  The Indonesian guests arrived here March 6. Besides Beijing, 
they are also scheduled to tour Shanghai. 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

<DOC>
<DOCNO> FBIS3-2274 </DOCNO>
